name: A Lowquestra em 3 Mvmts de Jazz
description: Lowquestra was written a few years ago, with each part being done bit by bit over the course of a few years. At the time, I was a bassist playing in some jazz groups, meeting Rio's city musicians and studying composition. I can't remember what was my first music, but this was one of mine first pieces which I understood the effort of creating structures. I dedicate this music to Fernando Grilo.
